1
00:00:01,421 --> 00:00:08,508
( mellow theme playing )

2
00:00:10,100 --> 00:00:11,550
News from Northern Equestria!

3
00:00:11,700 --> 00:00:13,550
Uh... your highness.

4
00:00:13,700 --> 00:00:14,330
Yes?

5
00:00:14,480 --> 00:00:18,280
I am simply to tell you that...
it has returned.

6
00:00:18,281 --> 00:00:19,281
( gasps )

7
00:00:19,560 --> 00:00:21,330
Find Princess Cadance and Shining Armor.

8
00:00:21,480 --> 00:00:22,830
Yes, your highness.

9
